All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AlbumIterator
Interface to iterate over photos in the album
Photo
A Photo has a name, filePath, dateAdded, and fileSize that can be retrieved
PhotoAlbumApp
A PhotoAlbumApp initializes the main application window and adds all MVC components to a JFrame
PhotoAlbumController
A PhotoAlbumController is a JPanel that contains buttons for adding, deleting, sorting, and navigating a photo album, responding to user actions and modifies the model
PhotoAlbumModel
A PhotoAlbumModel represents the photo collection and the current state of the album and notifies the view when there are changes.
PhotoAlbumView
A PhotoAlbumView provides a GUI that displays an updated list of photos and the current photo
SortByDate
A SortByDate Object is a SortingStrategy that uses a Comparator to sort a list of Photos by Date
SortByName
A SortByName Object is a SortingStrategy that uses a Comparator to sort a list of Photos by name
SortBySize
A SortBySize Object is a SortingStrategy that uses a Comparator to sort a list of Photos by fileSize
SortingStrategy
Interface to sort photos in the album by a characteristic of Photos
